{"tid":587712,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［肥絲入］蒞 定 嚟？？","createTime":"2018-03-10T15:38:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-11T13:11:59.000Z","uid":109598,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"10292a3b6e7b59958a815cdfd06f3f58744465f1","tid":587712,"uid":109598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T15:38:24.000Z","msg":"真心問"},{"pid":"05f0d3ba5b5aada75d65ebc2febc54081d719d97","tid":587712,"uid":21423,"like":13,"dislike":4,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T15:45:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"34b6bdde5f1d66c4806446c5de475f33ff18caf2","tid":587712,"uid":33420,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T15:49:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>清代粵語韻書《分韻撮要》記錄「蒞」字為陽去聲，「利」小韻。「蒞」字是陽去聲，和「利」字同音，而「嚟」字讀陽平聲，讀音不同，所以「嚟」的本字不是「蒞」。「嚟」的本字很簡單，不過是「來」的白讀。「來」的文讀是loi4，白讀lei4。［注三］「來」多數表逹文讀音loi4，為免誤會所以另做新字「嚟」來表白讀音lei4。「嚟」字通行後，大家反而不知道「來」有白讀音lei4。王禹偁《揚州寒食》：「今年蒞淮海，時節又清明。」「蒞」應解作面臨之義，而非解作來到。《康熙字典》引《韻會》：「莅，臨也。」是其義。</blockquote><br />\n肥c <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c00339c5fbb910c17fad99314d1d4f43ae658d14","tid":587712,"uid":7343,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T15:50:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/10/205655_cb3cef481c87a431cde5a1f38369155d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F10%2F205655_cb3cef481c87a431cde5a1f38369155d.png&h=9a7072e5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8482df6b439e10414b54635bb25ec48912593fdf","tid":587712,"uid":58841,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"05f0d3ba5b5aada75d65ebc2febc54081d719d97","tid":587712,"uid":21423,"like":13,"dislike":4,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T15:45:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T15:50:52.000Z","msg":"九撚唔搭八<br />\n講重點啦"},{"pid":"a0cb398b1be7566f412a28f11a9efd07927583c4","tid":587712,"uid":21423,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"repl